title: Video: Kitty Pryde – ☠DEAD❤ISLAND☠
content:
Ten years from now, media theorists will study Kitty Pryde and the affect that her rapping had on the music industry and the cultural sphere as a whole.

From describing her as ‘going viral’ to ‘an outcast white girl’, what all their years of work and attempts to categorise the pint-sized rapper will ultimately boil down to, is that she’s REALLY good. Her newest teaser track ☠DEAD❤ISLAND☠ (emoticons intentional) is only going to serve to build hype around the nineteen year old, and her upcoming EP D.A.I.S.Y. Rage. Check out the clip below, described by Kitty herself as ‘the sparkliest video of all time’.
